(1, '', 'Homes', 'Inicios', 'Madagascar Tours: Explore Nature\'s Wonders Today!', 'Turismo responsable en Madagascar - Madagascar Green Tours', 'Explore unforgettable Madagascar tours with us today!', 'Descubre el turismo responsable en Madagascar y su belleza.', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'img/uploads/images/img_6860cc03255275.94486811.webp', 'Descover Madagacar with us', 'Descubra Madagascar con nosotros!', 'Welcome to Madagascar Green Tours', 'Bienvenido a Madagascar Green Tours', 'The reliable travel agency Receptive Local Tour Operator', 'La agencia de viajes confiable Operador turístico receptivo y Compañía de gestión de destinos para sus viajes en Madagascar', '  <p>Discover Madagascar your way with Madagascar Green Tours - a multi-award-winning\r\n                            English-speaking tour operator. We design unforgettable, tailor-made journeys across the\r\n                            island, personalized to your interests and budget. Whether you\'re dreaming of pristine\r\n                            beaches, lush rainforests, or cultural adventures, we’ll craft the perfect itinerary just\r\n                            for you. Tour operator specializing in classic birdwatching and group tours in Madagascar,\r\n                            catering to traveler from various countries.</p>\r\n                        <p></p>\r\n                        <p>Madagascar Green Tours a tour operator in Madagascar with a goal\r\n                            to give satisfaction of clients and meet their needs ,undoubtedly helps you discover\r\n                            all the facets of the country. Being in the heart of the Indian ocean , located\r\n                            geographically\r\n                            between mainland Africa and Asia, this paradisiacal Island that has a lot to offer stretches\r\n                            from North to South , From the intact beaches of the Mitsio</p>\r\n                        <p>Madagascar Green Tours expressing readiness to receive people of\r\n                            all Nationalities and with 25 years of experience exploring the Island .\r\n                            never misses to provide possibilities to discover fauna and flora that are mostly\r\n                            endemic plus the kindness of the people with their culture which still remains\r\n                            unforgettable.</p>\r\n<h5 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center; \">Guided tour in Madagascar with our private local guides\r\n                        </h5>', '  <p class=\"text-justify fs-13\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">Madagascar Green Tours un tour operador en Madagascar con el objetivo de dar satisfacción a los clientes y satisfacer sus necesidades, sin duda te ayuda a descubrir todas las facetas del país. Estando en el corazón del océano Índico, ubicada geográficamente entre África continental y Asia, esta isla paradisíaca que tiene mucho que ofrecer se extiende de norte a sur, desde las intactas playas del Mitsio</p><p class=\"text-justify fs-13\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">Madagascar Green Tours expresando su disposición a recibir personas de todas las Nacionalidades y con 20 años de experiencia explorando la Isla, nunca deja de brindar posibilidades para descubrir fauna y flora que en su mayoría son endémicas más la amabilidad de la gente con su cultura que aún sigue siendo inolvidable.</p><p class=\"text-justify fs-13\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">Solo ten en cuenta que un viaje a Madagascar nunca te deja indiferente. Podemos organizar un tour privado y circuitos turísticos a medida, somos un operador turístico especializado en observación clásica de aves y tours en grupo en Madagascar, atendiendo a viajeros de varios países.<br></p><h4 class=\"text-center\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Visita guiada por Madagascar con nuestros guías locales privados</h4>', '2025-06-17 08:26:20', '2025-06-22 13:34:56'),
(10, 'tours', 'Our tours', 'Nuestras tours', 'Madagascar Eco-Friendly Excursions | Green Tours', 'Excursiones culturales en Madagascar | Madagascar Green Tours', 'Discover Madagascar eco-friendly excursions for a sustainable adventure.', 'Descubre emocionantes excursiones culturales en Madagascar.', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'img/uploads/images/img_68635c2429b843.85222071.webp', 'Here our popular tours', 'Estos son los famosos recorridos', 'Awesome tours', 'Bienvenido a Madagascar Green Tours', 'hello world', 'La agencia de viajes confiable Operador turístico receptivo y Compañía de gestión de destinos para sus viajes en Madagascar', '<p>sdq</p>', '<p>sdq</p>', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(11, 'reviews', 'Reviews', 'Reseñas', 'Madagascar Travel Reviews - Explore Authentic Experiences', 'Opiniones sobre tours en Madagascar - Madagascar Green Tours', 'Discover authentic Madagascar travel reviews and tips.', 'Descubre opiniones sobre tours en Madagascar y elige tu aventura ideal.', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', '', 'Please submit your comments, suggestions and other miscellaneous questions below. These remarks are very important for us to always better satisfy you in the organization of your travels. If you come back from a trip with Madagascar Green Tours, tell us your impressions! And look what our clients said about our services', 'Envíe sus comentarios, sugerencias y otras preguntas a continuación. Estas observaciones son muy importantes para que podamos ofrecerle la mejor satisfacción en la organización de sus viajes. Si regresa de un viaje con Madagascar Green Tours, ¡cuéntenos sus impresiones! Y vea lo que nuestros clientes opinan sobre nuestros servicios.', 'Reviews of mdagascar green tours', 'Reviews of mdagascar green tours', 'Reviews of mdagascar green tours', 'Reviews of mdagascar green tours', '<p><span style=\"text-align: center;\">Please submit your comments, suggestions and other miscellaneous questions below. These remarks are very important for us to always better satisfy you in the organization of your travels. If you come back from a trip with Madagascar Green Tours, tell us your impressions! And look what our clients said about our services</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"text-align: center;\">Please submit your comments, suggestions and other miscellaneous questions below. These remarks are very important for us to always better satisfy you in the organization of your travels. If you come back from a trip with Madagascar Green Tours, tell us your impressions! And look what our clients said about our services</span></p>', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(12, 'blogs', 'Blogs', 'Blogs', 'Madagascar Sustainable Tourism: Explore Eco-Friendly Travel', 'Experiencias culturales en Madagascar: Descubre más', 'Discover the benefits of Madagascar sustainable tourism.', 'Descubre las mejores experiencias culturales en Madagascar.', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'img/uploads/images/img_6863cc5a18a3a5.53846756.webp', 'Here our Blogs', 'Aquí nuestros blogs', '', '', '', '', '<p>sdq</p>', '<p>sdq</p>', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(13, 'sales-conditions', 'Sales condition', 'Condiciones de venta', 'Madagascar Trip Policies - Essential Travel Information', 'Condiciones de venta Madagascar - Madagascar Green Tours', 'Discover essential Madagascar trip policies for your journey.', 'Condiciones de venta Madagascar para tus viajes.', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', '', 'Conditions of sale for the tourist services', 'Condiciones de venta de los servicios turísticos', 'Conditions of sale for the tourist services', 'Conditions of sale for the tourist services', 'Conditions of sale for the tourist services', 'Conditions of sale for the tourist services', '<h4 class=\"fontMedium text-success mt-4\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 1.5rem !important;\">Registration and reservation</h4><p class=\"text-justify fontRegular\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">Registration or reservation for a circuit organized by Madagascar Green Tours can be done with our customer advisers at our agency in Antsirabe, or by e-mail at info@madagascar-green-tours.com When booking, specific information about the customer (first and last names, dates of birth, flight details, etc.) is required.</p><h4 class=\"fontMedium text-success\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Price</h4><p class=\"text-justify fontRegular mb-3\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 1rem !important;\">All tours sold by Madagascar Green Tours are priced in Euros or Dollars per person and cover the current year. The prices of the circuits offered by Madagascar Green Tours include only the services indicated in each offer. The descriptive sheets of Madagascar Green Tours trips and stays mention what is included in the price and what is not.<br>We may find ourselves obliged to modify our prices and our programs to take into account:</p><ul class=\"fontRegular\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- variations in the cost of transport, linked in particular to the cost of fuel.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- changes in fees and taxes relating to the services provided, such as taxes</li></ul><h4 class=\"fontMedium text-success mt-4\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 1.5rem !important;\">Rules</h4><p class=\"fontRegular\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">Any reservation of a place for a circuit must be accompanied by a deposit of 20% of the price of the service after receipt of the invoice by email, payable by bank transfer, and net of costs for the Agency. The payment of this deposit will confirm the customer\'s registration. As soon as the transfer is sent, a copy of the transfer order and a copy of your bank\'s address must be sent to us for follow-up.<br>The balance must then be paid in cash on the date of arrival.</p><h4 class=\"fontMedium text-success\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Cancelation</h4><p class=\"fontRegular mb-2\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">Before the journey If the customer has to cancel his trip, the sums paid will be refunded subject to the following penalties, depending on the date of withdrawal:</p><ul class=\"fontRegular\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- If canceled more than 3 months before departure: 10% of the total price of the trip</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- If canceled 90 to 31 days before departure: 20% of the total price of the trip</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- From 30 to 21 days before departure: 50% of the total price of the trip</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- From 20 to 10 days before departure: 75% of the total price of the trip</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- Less than 9 days before departure: 100% of the total price of the trip</li></ul><p class=\"fontRegular mb-0\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">Before the journey If the customer has to cancel his trip, the sums paid will be refunded subject to the following penalties, depending on the date of withdrawal:</p><ul class=\"fontRegular a\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- If the minimum number of participants is not reached</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- If the necessary payments have not been made in time</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- In case of force majeure (climate, air transport, etc.)</li></ul><p class=\"fontRegular\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">The terms of reimbursement mentioned above cannot be applied in the event that the reservation of services involves the commitment, on the part of Madagascar Green Tours, of expenses which cannot be reimbursed whatever the reason for the cancellation or the anticipation with which it is formulated (such as the purchase of certain plane tickets, the reservation of hotel packages on particular dates, etc.).<br>In the event of a change in the number of participants, the prices will be revised and adapted.</p>', '<h4 class=\"fontMedium text-success mt-4\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 1.5rem !important;\">Inscripción y reserva</h4><p class=\"text-justify fontRegular\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">La inscripción o reserva de un circuito organizado por Madagascar Green Tours puede hacerse con nuestros asesores de atención al cliente en nuestra agencia de Antsirabe, o por correo electrónico a info@madagascar-green-tours.com En el momento de la reserva, la información específica sobre el cliente (nombre y apellidos, fechas de nacimiento, datos del vuelo, etc.).</p><h4 class=\"fontMedium text-success\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Precio</h4><p class=\"text-justify fontRegular mb-3\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 1rem !important;\">Todos los tours vendidos por Madagascar Green Tours tienen precios en euros o dólares por persona. y cubrir el año en curso. Los precios de los circuitos ofrecidos por Madagascar Green Tours incluir únicamente los servicios indicados en cada oferta. Las hojas descriptivas de Los viajes y estancias de Madagascar Green Tours mencionan lo que está incluido en el precio y lo que no.<br>Podemos vernos obligados a modificar nuestros precios y nuestros programas para tener en cuenta:</p><ul class=\"fontRegular\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- variaciones del coste del transporte, relacionadas en particular con el coste del combustible.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">- cambios en tarifas e impuestos relacionados con los servicios prestados, como impuestos</li></ul><h4 class=\"fontMedium text-success mt-4\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; mar