(369, 5, 'Carlos Vazquez', 'cvazquezampa@gmail.com', 'We had an unforgettable experience with Madagascar Green Tours, led by Baba Solomon.\r\nHe designed the perfect trip for us, tailored to our preferences, combining nature, people, history, and culture.\r\n\r\nA special mention goes to the two people who accompanied us: our guide, Tsiory, who spoke perfect Spanish and always looked after our well-being. He adapted the daily plans whenever needed, gave us lots of extra explanations to help us better understand life in the country, and brought the passion of someone who truly loves their work. And our driver, Alain, who drove us everywhere with great professionalism and skill, despite the challenges of traveling around the country. Their dedication was key to making our 13 days in Madagascar truly memorable.\r\n\r\nWe would also like to highlight the excellent local partners that Madagascar Green Tours works with in all the National Parks, which made our visits even richer.\r\n\r\nIn short, this is a company we can wholeheartedly recommend—one that truly puts the traveler’s experience at the center of everything they do.', 0, '2025-09-02 08:22:56'),
